erval, respectively (0 &#x02013; no recombination, 1 &#x02013; recombination), <italic>k</italic> denotes the replicate line, and <italic>p</italic><sub><italic>ijk</italic></sub> and <italic>n</italic><sub><italic>ijk</italic></sub> represent the probability and the observed number of individuals of the genotype class <italic>ij</italic> in replicate line <italic>k</italic> in the backcross progeny (within control or selection). The frequencies for the four genotype classes were defined as:<disp-formula id="Equb"><alternatives><tex-math id="M3">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
